    "title": "Career Opportunity Real Estate Agent at Nexus Malls Global Group",
    "description": "Nexus Malls Global Group has an exciting opening for a Real Estate Agent at our Visakhapatnam office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Nexus Malls Global Group:\nNexus Malls Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Client Relationship Management\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nexus Malls Global Group!",
